casebody.data:
Hinkle et al., Appellants, v. Cleveland Clinic Foundation, Appellee.

[Cite as Hinkle v. Cleveland Clinic Found., 108 Ohio St.3d 1209, 2006-Ohio-551.]

(No. 2005-0334 Submitted December 14, 2005 Decided February 22, 2006.) Douglas S. Roberts; and Becker & Mishkind Co., L.P.A., Michael F. Becker, and David A. Kulwicki, for appellants. Roetzel & Andress, Anna Moore Carulas, Ingrid Kinkopf-Zajac, and Douglas G. Leak, for appellee.

{¶ 1} The cause is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently accepted.

Moyer, C.J., Resnick, Pfeifer, Lundberg Stratton, O’Connor, O’Donnell and Lanzinger, JJ., concur.
